ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Thaidene Nene (East Arm of Great Slave Lake) National Park Reserve) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (THAIDENE NENE (EAST ARM OF GREAT SLAVE LAKE) NATIONAL PARK RESERVE) ORDER in order to (1) repeal the existing Order in Council P.C. 2007-1659 of November 1, 2007 and (2) make a new Order to facilitate the establishment of a national park in the Thaidene Nene (East Arm of Great Slave Lake) area in the Northwest Territories.
